  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study should create data for the selection of a clinically relevant primary endpoint to
      assess the efficacy and safety of Buparid/PARI SINUS as compared to Budes Nasal Spray in the
      therapy of chronic rhinosinusitis (CRS) with polyposis nasi in adult patients. Ideally, the
      selected parameter should allow a correlation between an objective methodology and the
      clinical outcome of the study patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
